snippet.title: Taram Baba Demo: Next Fest Update Trailer
snippet.description:
It's almost time for Steam Next Fext, and we're very excited to participate. 

Grab your pistol and plunge into the dark. Try out our demo in the week-long festival!

Try Taram Baba Demo on Steam!

Link to the demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3516750/Taram_Baba_Demo/

Wishlist the full game;
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3420790/Taram_Baba/

Join us and express your opinions on Discord:
https://t.co/tOPYMVclMt

Join our community on Reddit:
https://www.reddit.com/r/BookClubExperimental/

Follow us on Twitter:
https://x.com/BookClubX
